 Also, task-like monads (such as 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

Future
\end_layout

\end_inset

) and the external side-effect monads (such as 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

IO
\end_layout

\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

ZIO
\end_layout

\end_inset

