The pass/fail monads (such as 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

Option
\end_layout

\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

Try
\end_layout

\end_inset

