 the effects of the same monad, or we run the effects of the other monad.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In the first case, we lift a value 
\begin_inset Formula $m:M^{A}$
\end_inset

 to the stack 
\begin_inset Formula $T_{L}^{M}$
\end_inset

