\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\text{flift}_{L}\bef\text{frun}_{L}(\theta_{M}):M^{A}\rightarrow L^{A}\quad.
\]

\end_inset

Note that both 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

flift
\end_layout

\end_inset

