T_{K}^{M,A} & \bbnum 0 & \text{frun}_{K}^{M,M^{\prime}}\!(\phi)
\end{array}\,=(a\rightarrow a+\bbnum 0^{:T_{K}^{M,A}})\bef\,\begin{array}{|c||cc|}
