T_{K}^{M,A} & \bbnum 0 & \text{frun}_{K}^{M,M^{\prime}}\!(\phi)
\end{array}^{\uparrow M}\bef\gunderline{\phi\bef\theta_{P^{\prime}}^{\uparrow M^{\prime}}}\bef\text{ftn}_{M^{\prime}}\\
