\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \text{pu}_{T}^{\uparrow L}\bef\text{prod}=(\text{pu}_{L}\bef\text{pu}_{M})^{\uparrow L}\bef\text{prod}\\
 & =\,\begin{array}{|c||cc|}
