\text{uncu}:\left(A\rightarrow B\rightarrow C\right)\rightarrow A\times B\rightarrow C\quad,\quad\quad\text{uncu}\left(f\right)\triangleq a^{:A}\times b^{:B}\rightarrow f(a)(b)\quad,
\]

