\begin_inset Formula $\_^{:\bbnum 1}\rightarrow\text{wu}_{R}$
\end_inset

 is indeed an isomorphism between the types 
\begin_inset Formula $\bbnum 1$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $R^{\bbnum 1}$
\end_inset

