\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

simple
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 operation 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

scop
\end_layout

\end_inset

 in the codensity monad 
\begin_inset Formula $\text{Cod}^{M}$
\end_inset

.
 We define 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

scop
\end_layout

\end_inset

