\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Since the monad 
\begin_inset Formula $M$
\end_inset

 is injectively embedded within 
\begin_inset Formula $\text{Cod}^{M}$
\end_inset

 via the functions 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

inC
\end_layout

\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

outC
\end_layout

\end_inset

