\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\text{cc}_{P}\triangleq\text{scc}\bef p\bef\text{ftn}_{P}\quad.
\]

\end_inset

It remains to express 
\begin_inset Formula $\text{callcc}_{P}$
\end_inset

